Name: swap.orders
Description: Signed orders, compatible with each other, that will constitute the swap

Name: swap.feeToken
Description: Token to be used to pay fees

Name: swap.amounts (optional)
Description: Actual amounts to be swapped (defaults to amounts in orders, if they are not limit orders)

Name: swap.fee (optional)
Description: Amount of token to be paid as a fee for this transaction.https://merlin-li.github.io/zksync/api/js/accounts#fn5

Name: swap.nonce (optional)
Description: Nonce that is going to be used for this transaction.https://merlin-li.github.io/zksync/api/js/accounts#fn7
